        @ByVal
public static LargeListArrayResult FromArrays(@Const @ByRef
                                                     Array offsets,
                                                     @Const @ByRef
                                                     Array values,
                                                     MemoryPool pool)
        \brief Construct LargeListArray from array of offsets and child value array This function does the bare minimum of validation of the offsets and input types, and will allocate a new offsets array if necessary (i.e. if the offsets contain any nulls). If the offsets do not have nulls, they are assumed to be well-formed
        Parameters:
        offsets - [in] Array containing n + 1 offsets encoding length and size. Must be of int64 type
        values - [in] Array containing list values
        pool - [in] MemoryPool in case new offsets array needs to be allocated because of null values
